Winter Olympics 1992:
   Games Stats: Nordic Skiing
-- Length of Eddie "The Eagle" Edwards' longest jump: 102
meters (non-regulation jump, landed on head).
                                                                                                       

   -- Percentage of cross-country skiing medals won by
Soviets in 1988 Calgary Games: 67.
                                                                                                       

   -- Number of Olympic medals won by Americans in nordic
events: 1 (Bill Koch, 1976, Silver, 30 km cross-country).
                                                                                                       

